{"tid":2339291,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔止係暖男爸爸】假使聖誕原來不像你預期","createTime":"2020-12-24T14:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T11:34:56.000Z","uid":245286,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1b45e0baf51a75b4c33380c892bad6ed27912b2b","tid":2339291,"uid":245286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"雖然喺暖男爸爸post擺過，但係我覺得呢個要分享出嚟畀到多啲人睇，因為係一條講咗好多嘢嘅片～<br />\n<br />\n導演同演員，重有剪片都好用心，趕到今日完成再upload喺中基嘅YouTube Channel度，希望冇睇過暖男爸爸嘅巴絲都可以撳入去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J12PE-2OKdw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ12PE-2OKdw&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=7d51e279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J12PE-2OKdw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6oyvV1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6oyvV1.png&h=208b3b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNYiG2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNYiG2G.png&h=9df11d19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f93ad198689a33ea5078f88073035849db4a579","tid":2339291,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063150a46b32c582e39a422c51567aab806b8655","tid":2339291,"uid":193840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:38:39.000Z","msg":"好正"},{"pid":"cf5d5dbc8ce9c525d02d6dd9f0dc7af2bf08844c","tid":2339291,"uid":1072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b06ad51743f6fa8d4f91210095593ffd66e365f","tid":2339291,"uid":155778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"好有意思，要推比多d人睇"},{"pid":"5534dd1c772d408129082857a9eaa4f09c2e710f","tid":2339291,"uid":221571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"知咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4895e5c46a57a24e4226e423268035994dc9e5","tid":2339291,"uid":2730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117909cc2c31dbcc1be80c83795b2b30f33c9dcb","tid":2339291,"uid":245286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"影片簡介係一段影片自古以嚟不可分割嘅一部份，而家擺埋上嚟：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我（註：即係中基）的話：<br />\n今年疫情令大家都過得好困難，好開心套劇能夠帶比香港人咁多歡笑與眼淚（使用咗咁多你哋啲紙巾，我一啲都唔後悔，仲有啲沾沾添😌）。原先諗住同導演Peter重新陳設便利店等大家可以聖誕節去打卡架嘛，DKLM 點知疫情又嚴重咗，咁我哋費事要大家冒險啦，所以大膽搵返啲演員一齊開開心心做件事。有個偉人曾經講過：「冇比較就冇傷害。所以冇經歷過挫折同障礙就唔會感受到平凡係幾值得珍惜。」祝大家聖誕快樂、身體健康🎄珍惜眼前人，感恩現在所擁有，然後繼續努力！<br />\nP.S. 唔好問我偉人係邊個<br />\n再P.S. 要短時間完成呢件事真係好難，要感謝Peter、剪片師同音樂部門Jeffrey呢幾日趕工先趕得切今晚出到街，比啲掌聲👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻<br />\n<br />\n導演的話：<br />\n2020年，香港人經歷咗好多苦難，甚至失去咗好多嘢，周圍嘅人和事可以一夜之間變到我哋都唔認得。不過响咁多荒謬同苦難之中，我又見到好多難得嘅團結、堅持同希望。<br />\n到咗年底，眼見我哋可能連聖誕節都會失去埋，於是我有一個好傻嘅諗法，可唔可以拍一個故事將聖誕節同埋聖誕所代表嘅平安、溫暖同希望都帶返俾香港人。呢件咁傻嘅事居然得到一班好朋友無條件嘅支持，令我超級感動之餘，再次相信只要我哋唔放棄希望，希望就唔會放棄我哋。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cf0c274b32f64b514a9dabac6d4a107368a0c7fd","tid":2339291,"uid":351771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd84058e9608f64ab17761142411d8368ce7cc4","tid":2339291,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"其實幾sad"},{"pid":"1371894cc16d9e9dde4c4b135601f540d8b1633e","tid":2339291,"uid":15730,"like":2,"disli